I’ve been getting alot of anxiety, especially at night so I’ve had trouble sleeping. Sometimes i forget about my interests and who i am. So a day to myself was much needed (and a foot massage lol). A day to just not think. Be gentle with yourself and kind to others 🫶❤️ #vlog #selfcare #cooking #mentalhealth
